<p class="ql-align-justify">『巨型火山牛肉丼』来了</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">份量变态！肉多到看不见饭！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>300g牛肉，360°堆成山</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>澳洲和牛肉，现点现烧</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">一不小心还会爆浆</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">...</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>东京的「烧肉丼专门店」</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200916/dfa9286c885749e78d7f25193fe6d1f2.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200916/81f7bc7675024394adb82c48f53d79b4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>有10年经验的京炎主厨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200916/ec54eff5ea6242efb8e6e5c2aca0b507.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200916/e1f9407cb3254a2bb8d433d862c926f7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200916/15a686b265814a49b200e22b4f002113.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">店内所有的菜品出自有<strong>10年料理经验的师傅</strong>之手，从选材到制作都层层把关。<strong>明档现烤现吃</strong>，还原正宗日式丼饭风味。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>京炎吃到的每一口，都让你惊艳</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200916/ad524b0278de431694ce991e9b1eb6c1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">超高的性价比让许多人来一次就爱上「京炎」，<strong>新鲜食材、正宗日式风味、碗碗料多到爆棚</strong>，一口就足以惊艳味蕾！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200916/27461843caf64e0191d995718160fe95.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>大满贯牛丼｜炎炙蟹肉丼｜京炎炎杂锦串</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>炎烤墨鱼肠｜黑椒岩盐烤蘑菇</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">主打「巨型火山丼饭」，肉都爆爆爆了</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">大满贯牛丼</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">グランドスラム牛丼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200916/b3d7d2ce7dd84fb98c89c3e6d54869db.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">第一次来「京炎」，必定要点上一碗<strong>大满足牛丼</strong>！肉肉多到堆成小山，一上桌就自带吸睛属性，过足你的肉瘾～</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200916/a05304859bce4fe8a7b18abd25dc01ba.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200916/1d4ddfb48dfa4783b919380a0f4f31f6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">被<strong>澳洲和牛肉360°包围</strong>的牛肉丼，这么多肉肉已经值回一半票价！但即便如此平正靓的牛肉丼，京炎却一点也不马虎，所有食材都要用最好的！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>顶级澳洲和牛肉，现点现烧</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200916/037bf89160454e57ac0ecb33e518b88f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">烤肉丼饭，肉的品质至关重要，只用<strong>澳洲顶级和牛肉</strong>，满满一大盘是一份牛肉丼的肉量，牛肉控这下真的大满足啦～</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200916/8f3063aabc204e138d1bd8e92ef3bb56.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200916/1da36d5ca9e041bab3ab5e8bc43927da.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>300°炭火高温快烧，肉汁被紧紧锁住</strong>，加上秘制烧肉汁，保留些许粉嫩，此时是最佳口感，入口软嫩不腥，味蕾暴击！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>只用罗永浩力荐的龙米家</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200916/ccff6978246e467e9209e0a6a3b442fe.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200916/0f7cdcc4271f4b369b2c7bc7b2896545.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200916/505a01287edd4bfda62ee1303a79cfc3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">丼饭的米也大有讲究，只用<strong>众多高端日料店才会用的“龙米”</strong>。煮出来的饭粒粒饱满，略带嚼劲，米香味清新馥郁，单单吃米饭的话也觉得满足。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>刺身级别的“兰皇蛋”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200916/d06ecbb07ec142278aa4738d6d513181.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200916/a1adfa4f604c402fa977f6d7b2f3b4f3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">丼饭顶部的鸡蛋用的是拥有70年养殖经验的刺身级别<strong>“兰皇蛋”</strong>，没有一丝蛋腥味，用来拌饭滑嫩又鲜甜！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200916/ecfafff9b50f46c0987bfba9a4256f8c.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">每颗鸡蛋都有属于自己的“身份证”，新鲜安全有保障。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>肉量爆棚，教你这3种吃法</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>①先吃澳洲和牛肉，感受原汁原味</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200916/8ba27ecc93af4dbe881923865c3fd402.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>②捅破顶部的兰皇蛋搅拌，更鲜甜</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200916/21948d4b3ee94c8791d9167dade81196.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200916/76ccc8bd73974b2ab991c28f2325cc03.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>③加上米饭一起入口，感受多重口感</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200916/0221cf89ce274b119ecfacc79b393d4e.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200916/faf05a32670649298882d1c0bce23d1d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">澳洲和牛肉带着炙烤的香气，入口<strong>鲜甜多汁</strong>，加上鸡蛋搅拌着吃，软嫩的口感up！最后和龙米一起送入口中，这种吃法让人完全无法拒绝，够过瘾！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>胃小的选“女神款”，肉量不减</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200916/decc0d0a904746e0a1e8adcbd95b34e1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">如果是胃小或者不爱吃米饭的女生，可以尝试这款女神版大满足牛丼，<strong>饭量减少但肉量丝毫不减！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200916/e509d735145e45fead649060dfe33f85.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200916/72cbcdf5cd254585892c6a9a0275607a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">澳洲和牛肉泛着诱人油光，恰到好处的熟度透出嫩粉。筷子一夹，<strong>肉的下面还是肉</strong>，实打实分量足！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>鹅肝牛舌丼饭</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">フォアグラ牛タン丼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200916/d753e17dd2574435883032d7f88ea0e8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>一面是细腻的鹅肝、一面是饱满的牛舌</strong>，厚厚一层铺在米饭表面，双重满足！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200916/9cb934999c3341dd8ae5416ee1b49130.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200916/929902e45e0a446d80ad404e9e6726fb.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200916/1ceff5f54458498f838baaf568ac59fd.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>高温炭火逼出鹅肝的油脂</strong>，表面微微焦，细腻的口感被激发！而牛舌现烤后，变得更加爽脆，肉香、奶香、油脂香，在口中不停地回荡～</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200916/dbd004d319694a85abc5a3f43abfe021.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200916/ab150dbdb98d4c72bda018e44ea5debe.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>一块绵软的鹅肝，一丝解腻的高丽菜</strong>，一勺香气浓郁的米饭，生活的疲惫随着这一口满足消散～</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>炎炙蟹肉丼</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">炙かに肉丼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200916/7504cd1806824330a63108a956f75c0e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>蟹肉+鱼籽堆成小山的丼饭</strong>，浓郁的鲜甜味道，一口满满炙香的蟹肉超级满足！表面的酱汁是点睛之笔，增添了不少奶香味。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200916/655537c0223043dbbb648143c8f84503.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200916/007cc1f7d25e42f4a88846b7a17800d6.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200916/f2d81541bcff4037941efe1422c17b28.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">喷枪快速火烤，酱汁融进蟹肉里，<strong>散发着淡淡炙烤的味道</strong>，又是这该死的迷人味道，比回家的诱惑还诱惑。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200916/46885c6796694aeb8c5adf383130555e.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200916/face993eea91487ca51e20959bfe04cf.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200916/6940486ddd9644fca36b8ce6e48aa479.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">炙烤后的蟹肉肉质变得更加紧实，和鱼籽搅拌均匀，一口下去，<strong>鱼籽在舌尖颗颗爆开</strong>，这谁顶得住嘛？！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>AMAZING</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>50+种日式料理，点上这些算你会吃</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>京炎六贯寿司盛</strong></p>
